---
title: One-Pan Beef, Black Bean ’n’ Rice Skillet with Mexican Spice Crema & Cilantro
description: This dish is everything you love about a burrito, sans tortilla, all in one lucky pan (hello, easy cleanup)! You’ll brown hearty ground beef with our savory Mexican spice blend, then add black beans and rice, and allow the flavors to bubble and meld. Serve it right out of the pan with a sprinkle of chopped cilantro and dollops of spiced crema for tangy, creamy contrast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65d4ce1555fb9bf6391b6bc0-362f866c.jpeg
